programme.title: Aroma Tradisi S6 Ep13
programme.desc: Pengacara Chef Fikree menjelajah ke Kg. Kepala batas, Pulau Pinang melakukan aktiviti memasak bersama Ainon Abdul Wahab. programme.title: Hilangkah Janji Kita S1 Ep06
programme.desc: Izlyn dan anak-anak menghadapi kesukaran untuk meneruskan kehidupan setelah Reza menikahi Nisa.

programme.title: Cinta Kholdi
programme.desc: Cinta itu buta dan tidak mengenal warna kulit. Wani memperkenalkan Kholdi kepada ibu bapanya supaya mereka dapat menerima Kholdi sebagai menantu. Tapi malangnya sesuatu berlaku? Dapatkah Kholdi dan Wani bersatu.

programme.title: Huru Hara S14 Ep16
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai bersama barisan artis yang terdiri daripada Siqma, Sherry Ibrahim, Zeppo Youngsterz dan juga kugiran Motherwit.

programme.title: In Person S2 Ep11
programme.desc: Dalam rancangan In Person setiap episod membawa sekumpulan muzik tempatan tanah air yang berbeza dengan keunikan mereka yang tersendiri. Setiap episod menampilkan sesi temubual bersama ahli kumpulan secara mendalam dan rakaman persembahan mereka secara langsung.

programme.title: Pembancuh Kopi Mr Vampire S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Dr. Nadya terkejut dengan pengakuan Datin Sri Ayuni. Datin Sri Ayuni menyesal dengan apa yang dilakukannya kerana keputusannya itulah yang menyebabkan Irsyad jadi seperti sekarang. Dr. Nadya hanya diam. Datin Sri Ayuni meminta Dr. Nadya supaya merahsiakan hal ini dari pengetahuan Irsyad. Irsyad lebih banyak termenung. Terdapat banyak fail yang memerlukan tandatangan Irsyad yang dibawa oleh Irina. Safwan telah melaporkan kisah Nuzul yang diganggu oleh beberapa pemuda kampung kepada Ketua Kampung. Ketua Kampung menyelesaikan perkara tersebut dengan menegur sikap beberapa pemuda tersebut dan memberi amaran sekiranya hal ini berlaku sekali lagi, mereka semua akan dibawa ke balai. Irina melalui kesukaran dengan setiap kerjanya di pejabat kerana Irsyad masih belum mahu bekerjasama dan memberi tunjuk ajar. Irsyad masih lagi terbawa-bawa dengan perasaannya. Di kampung, dalam perjalanan pulang dari pekan, Safwan dan Nuha telah diserang oleh pemuda kampung yang mahu membalas dendam terhadap Safwan. Safwan telah ditumbuk dengan teruk dan Nuha hampir dirogol oleh mereka namun sempat diselamatkan oleh Safwan.

programme.title: Still Ep07
programme.desc: Ibu Laura meninggal dunia dan semua orang juga menghadapi kesedihan mereka sendiri. Sementara itu, Annette mendedahkan sesuatu yang sangat menyayat hati bagi Kulas dan ia merungkaikan mereka berdua. Kesemua mereka perlu menghadapi muzik seperti yang mereka katakan, tetapi tidak sebelum Kulas menyanyikan untuk mereka satu lagu terakhir untuk mendampingi dunia baru yang aneh ini. Mereka mengucapkan selamat tinggal kepada Balay, tempat mereka menemui rumah.

programme.title: Villa Angker Lembang
programme.desc: Kemal seorang lelaki muda yang berjaya, dia adalah pemilik sebuah syarikat broker saham yang besar dan mempunyai keluarga yang kecil dan bahagia. Dia dan isterinya, Citra merancang untuk membina perniagaan resort di tanah kosong di bandar Lembang, Kemal pergi ke kampung di sekitar tanahnya, dan secara tidak sengaja bertemu dengan Sujiwo, penjaga vila. Sujiwo menawarkannya sebuah resort lama dengan beberapa vila dan tanah besar di dalamnya yang telah ditinggalkan pemiliknya di luar negara. Lelaki itu memberi Kemal harga yang berpatutan untuk vila-vila itu berbanding jika Kemal terpaksa membina resort baru di atas tanah kosong yang memerlukan kos yang lebih tinggi. Kemal akhirnya memutuskan untuk membeli vila tersebut dan berhasrat untuk mengubahsuainya. Kemal, Citra bersama Satria (anaknya), dan Nadine (kakak iparnya), mereka pergi ke resort untuk percutian hujung minggu. Tidak lama kemudian, Kemal dan keluarga kecilnya menyedari bahawa vila itu berhantu. Mereka dihantui oleh figura menyeramkan yang membawa mereka ke bahagian paling gelap resort.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep04
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep27
programme.desc: Memaparkan dengan kehadiran abang Datin Umairah kini terungkai segalanya. Mizan tidak menyangka Syariff dua beradik dengan isterinya. Mizan kemudiannya bermaafan dengan Syariff dan Hani. Kini hubungan baik Mizan dan Hani tiada keraguan lagi. Perletakan jawatan Mizan juga tidak diterima syarikat. Mizan bercadang bercuti bersama Hani. Nizam yang keluar rumah terus diselubungi perasaan. Dia seolah-olah tidak dapat mengawal diri. Tanpa mengira Sheila begitu risau dan gagal mencarinya, Nizam ke rumah Hani. Mizan tiada ketika itu. Hani baru nak menghubungi Mizan, Nizam tanpa kebenaran memasuki memegang Hani dan tetap mempercayai Hani dan Mizan masih berlakon dan tidak cintakan Mizan. Lantaran itu dia memaksa Hani bersamanya. Mizan muncul tepat pada masanya dan menjelaskan segalanya. Dari situ Mizan dan Hani menjemput Sheila. Mizan meminta Nizam memberi pendiriannya selepas memberi nasihat mengikut pendekatan dan tuntutan agama agar menerima Sheila. Sebelum apa-apa lagi, Sheila memohon kemaafan kepada Hani atas segala sangkaannya. Sheila dan Nizam akan berbincang lanjut selepas itu. Syariff pula mendapati Kalsom sesuai padanya. Sementara itu, Dato Fuad, bukan sebenarnya Dato, dia menumpang gelaran isterinya dan hanya makan gaji di syarikat itu. Dato Umairah (bukan Datin) tidak mahu menerimanya. Suraya pula terkejut Status Fuad dan terpaksa menerima. Dalam pada itu Ah Meng telah memaksa dengan kekerasan menugut dia kembalikan wangnya.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S16 Ep01
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10, Chef Naem, tukang masak Dapur Bujang akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat.

programme.title: Jodoh Sebelah Pintu S1 Ep06
programme.desc: Mona dapati tunang misterinya, Alang, seolah-olah mampu menghidu gerak gerinya. Along juga seolah ada banyak persamaan dengan Amirul, jiran baharunya. Dia cuba menyiasat latar belakang lelaki itu sehingga menimbulkan rasa cemburu Julia. Hubungan mereka bermasalah semula. Dr Norma berasa marah selepas mendapat surat cinta itu. Dia menyangka ada orang yang cuba mempersendakannya. Selepas membuat penyiasatan, dia telah menyalahsangka seorang pekerja sebagai puncanya. Badrul terpaksa menjadi orang tengah.

programme.title: Japanizi Going Going Gong Ep38
programme.desc: Japanizi Going Going Gong ialah pertunjukan permainan fizikal kanak-kanak Kanada dengan motif Jepun di mana peserta bersaing dengan rakan sepasukan menentang pasukan lain semasa mereka menangani halangan dan cabaran untuk menguji keupayaan mental, kekuatan, ketahanan dan kepintaran mereka.

programme.title: Trend Setter S4 Ep10
programme.desc: Trend Setter adalah rancangan mengenai tren, fesyen dan gaya hidup. Di mana Nabil Mahir akan berjumpa dengan orang orang yang bergaya dan dikenali dalam tren mereka.

programme.title: In Person S2 Ep02
programme.desc: Dalam rancangan In Person setiap episod membawa sekumpulan muzik tempatan tanah air yang berbeza dengan keunikan mereka yang tersendiri. Setiap episod menampilkan sesi temubual bersama ahli kumpulan secara mendalam dan rakaman persembahan mereka secara langsung.

programme.title: Marriage With Benefits Ep06
programme.desc: Aksan dan Gea menerima berita mengejutkan daripada Sonya dan pada masa yang sama seseorang yang tak dijangka muncul dalam hidup mereka. Seseorang yang pantas mendekati Gea.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S8 Ep08
programme.desc: Rancangan ini menampilkan chef naem yang akan mengajar cara-cara untuk membuat 2 hidangan istimewa iaitu Mee Ayam dan Telur Gulung dengan bermodalkan hanya Rm10.

programme.title: Rojak S5 Ep01
programme.desc: Rojak adalah sebuah rancangan yang membawa pelbagai jenis informasi yang mendedahkan orang awam kepada benda yang mereka tidak biasanya akan cuba dari eksperimen sosial, D.I.Y. dan lain-lain lagi. Dihoskan oleh Leaism.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep03
programme.desc: Memaparkan Puan Yasmin menawarkan kepada menantunya Sofia butik perniagaan yang ditutup sementara waktu untuk beliau memulakan perniagaan. Majlis resepsi dijangkakan dalam beberapa hari lagi, namun keluarga Sofia masih tidak mendapat jemputan. Ini menimbulkan curiga pada Sofia. Semasa berada dalam dewan resepsi, Amar ternampak kad jemputan perkahwinan majlis tersebut tercatat nama pengantin Amar dan Erina. Apabila Amar bertanya ibunya, Yasmin mahu anaknya menunaikan janjinya sebelum ini dan terpaksa mengikut kehendak ibunya. Erina tiba dari UK kerana majlis persandingan akan diadakan pada keesokan harinya. Amar dalam perjalanan balik bertemu Sofia, dia telah dipukul sehingga pengsan oleh orang suruhan Yasmin. Yasmin bertemu dengan Sofia, memberitahu mengenai mengenai pernikahan Erina dengan Amar. Sofia bersedih kerana Amar tidak pulang-pulang dan gagal dihubungi. Erina mulai syak sesuatu yang tidak baik mengenai perkahwinan mereka. Di akhir episod, Rusdi melawat Amar di hospital setelah diselamatkan apabila dijumpai pengsan. Mereka mengetahui rahsia majlis perkahwinan yang sedang dirancang oleh ibunya.

programme.title: Pbtb E-San Indy
programme.desc: Tongkham is a poor E-san [northeastern] young man whose dream is to be a famous movie director and, while waiting for the first dream to come true, he also wants to get married to Pranee who left to work abroad. Thongkham dearly raises a fighting chicken Pranee gave him before she went away. The series of his misfortunes start when a friend steals his chicken and turns it into a dish for one afternoons usual drinking party. That is when Pranee comes back with her Swedish boyfriend who claims he is a director of real big films. What can Tongkham do to change her heart when he only has his fun loving fellow local villagers by his side?

programme.title: Pembancuh Kopi Mr Vampire S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Safwan dikerjakan ke hospital untuk dirawat. Nuha disoal-siasat oleh pihak polis. Nuzul, Nurin, Nazrul dan ibu Safwan bergegas ke hospital. Nuzul bersyukur kerana tiada apa-apa yang berlaku pada Safwan dan Nuha. Dia rasa bersalah kerana semuanya berpunca darinya. Safwan tidak menyalahkan sesiapa. Pemuda-pemuda yang menyerangnya juga sudah ditangkap oleh orang kampung dan dibawa ke balai polis. Sepanjang Safwan di hospital, Nuhalah yang banyak menjaganya kerana Nuzul bekerja dan perlu menjaga Nazrul. Irina dan Irham membawa Irsyad ke pusat fisioterapi. Doktor Johan memulakan sesinya bersama Irsyad. Dr. Nadya juga berada di situ untuk memantau Irsyad. Irina memeriksa setiap fail yang belum ditandatangani oleh Irsyad. Dia mula bengang kerana Irsyad masih tidak meneliti fail-fail penting. Irina pulang ke rumah dan mahu menyerang Irsyad dan dia sendiri sudah bosan untk melayan kerenah Irsyad hanya demi Nuzul. Sampai saja di rumah, Irina terus bergegas ke bilik Irsyad. Dia membuka pintu bilik dan terkejut melihat Irsyad yang sedang solat.

Entah mengapa, Ain rasa berdebar-debar setiap kali rapat dan diajar oleh Aidil untuk bermain permainan itu. Melissa bertanyakan soalan pelik kepada Ain mengapa Ain selalu excited bercerita tentang Aidil berbanding bakal tunangnya, Ryan.

Dia seakan hilang siapa dirinya hingga meresahkan orang-orang di sekeliling. Namun, dia menafikan bahawa dirinya sakit. Joshua pula sanggup bertindak mencederakan Myra setelah Myra berterus terang dengan Lukman dan Budi mengenai apa sebenarnya yang berlaku. Nazim pulang ke kampung untuk urusan pernikahan adiknya. Dia benar-benar tawar hati meskipun Lukman sudah insaf dan terus merayu agar Farah memberikan peluang kedua kepadanya.

Dia keluar dating dengan lelaki tetapi tiada seorang pun daripada mereka nampaknya membuat keputusan itu. Anda mungkin menyalahkan piawaiannya yang tinggi tetapi kesakitan akibat hubungannya sebelum ini juga boleh menjejaskan pertimbangannya terhadap lelaki. Kini, kehidupan cintanya mengalami kemarau selama tujuh tahun. Segalanya berubah apabila tiba-tiba, dua lelaki berminat untuk bersamanya. Ryan membeli cincin pertunangan daripada Chinggay hanya ditolak oleh teman wanitanya. Chinggay membantu Ryan untuk kembali dengan teman wanitanya tetapi mereka akhirnya kehilangan cincin dan menjadi kawan baik. Sebaliknya, bekas teman lelaki Chinggay, Frank, gigih untuk menebus dirinya dan membuktikan bahawa dia berhak mendapat peluang kedua bersama Chinggay. Irsyad cekalkan hati dan berusaha gigih untuk sembuh. Nuzul juga melalui fasa-fasa dalam hidupnya di kampung. Nuzul mula mencari kerja di bandar. Dia perlu mencari duit lebih kerana Nurin bakal melanjutkan pelajaran ke universiti. Satu hari, Nuzul pulang ke rumah dengan gembira kerana dia diterima bekerja sebagai kerani di Ipoh.

programme.desc: Mengenai pasangan muda yang miskin bekerja sebagai pembunuh upahan sehingga mereka diberi tugasan terbaru untuk menghapuskan abang isteri sendiri yang memaksa mereka lari dan bersembunyi daripada kumpulan itu untuk menyelamatkan diri dan bayi mereka.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Abang Man memperkenalkan Uzair tentang kehidupan di KL dengan mengajarnya tentang perlawanan di gelanggang haram dan mendapatkan Uzair pekerjaan di tempat cuci kereta. Di KL, Uzair bertemu semula dengan Ajeeb yang kini menjadi busker jalanan dan tinggal di bawah jambatan. Hatta datang untuk melawan Uzair di gelanggang haram untuk menyelesaikan hutang lama.

programme.title: Cadaver
programme.desc: Seon-hwa ialah pelajar baharu di sekolah perubatan elit, dan dia dimulakan ke kelas pembedahan yang diketuai oleh Dr. Han bersama lima pelajar lain, termasuk teman lelakinya Ki-beom. Selepas kelas pertama semua pelajar mula berkongsi mimpi ngeri yang sama melibatkan seorang pakar bedah bermata satu, dan satu demi satu mereka mula dibunuh, mangsa ditemui dengan hati mereka dikeluarkan. Seon-hwa dan Ki-beom yakin bahawa peristiwa ini berkaitan dengan mayat yang cantik dengan tatu mawar di payudaranya, dan mereka memulakan penyiasatan untuk mendedahkan identitinya.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep 15 Ep15
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Farish, Ryan dan Bakri masuk ke lokasi pemprosesan dadah kumpulan Samad. Mereka berjaya menumpaskan kumpulan tersebut. Tahir, selepas mendengar kesalahan yang dilakukan oleh adiknya Samad terpkasa melepaskan Haris dan Anuar dari kawalannya. Farish pula cuba menyelamatkan Kasandra dari tawanan Mazlan, dia berjaya membawa Kasandra keluar setelah helahnya menyamar sebagai peminat Kasandra telah membuat Mazlan tertipu. Dalam kes berasingan, Bakri sebagai bodyguard kepada Eira diminta berpura-pura menjadi teman lelaki Eira semasa mereka balik di kampung untuk berjumpa ibunya. Hakim pula telah menawan Yasmin dan pengurus pusat peranginan, Danial cuba mengesan kedudukan Yasmin dan Hakim.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep 16 Ep16
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Danial terpaksa menyelamatkan Yasmin dari tawanan Hakim. Hakim mengalami halunisasi akibat telah lama tidak mengambil ubat psikiatrik. Dato Bakri bapa kepada Yasmin dan Datin Rosnah ibu kepada Hakim akan berkahwin. Dalam kes berasingan, Mazlan telah ditangkap oleh orang-orang bodyguard Farish. Dia diberi amaran supaya tidak memaparkan gambar bogel Kasandra. Mazlan diberhentikan kerja sebagai Pengurus Kasandra. Eisha sepupu kepada Farish, meminta pertolongan ibu Farish memujuk supaya Farish bersetuju berkahwin dengannya. Akibatnya perhubungan Farish dengan Nasha menghadapi masalah. Bakri bodyguard Eira pulang ke kampung. Eira terpikat dengan Azlan, Sebaliknya Mak Mah terpikat dengan Bakri untuk dijodohkan dengan Eira. Dalam kes baru, Ryan bodyguard kepada seorang Dato menghadapi masalah dengan seorang perempuan simpanan.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep 17 Ep17
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kamal seorang kontraktor mahukan seorang bodyguard kerana dia selalu membawa wang tunai yang banyak, Ryan akan menjadi bodyguardnya. Suatu hari Ryan terkejut apabila mendapati teman wanita Kamal merupakan bekas teman wanitanya. Bakri pula diambil sebagai bodyguard Zara, kerana dia mahu mengelakkan diri daripada dipukul oleh teman lelakinya Taufik yang terlalu kuat cemburu. Farish bodyguard kepada Shamsul. apabila emaknya berkahwin semula dengan lelaki lebih muda, Shamsul keluar dari rumah kerana cemburu dengan bapa tirinya. Untuk sementara waktu dia tinggal bersama Farish. Dalam kes lain, Danial membantu Datin Noor melakukan perubahan fizikal melalui rawatan kecantikan. Di akhir episode, hubungan Farish semakin mesra dengan Nasha sehingga Farish menolak tawaran berkahwin dengan sepupunya Eisha

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep 18 Ep18
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ryan menjadi bodyguard kepada Kamal, dia terperanjat bila mendapati Salina teman wanitanya juga berkawan dengan Kamal. Kamal adalah bapa tiri kepada Shamsul. Farish menjadi bodyguard kepada Shamsul, mereka terperanjat apabila menjumpai Kamal bersama-sama dengan Salina. Shamsul mengambil gambar Kamal dan Salina, gambar ini dihantar kepada emaknya. Pada yang sama Kamal syak Ryan mempunyai hubungan dengan Salina. Dia meminta Nasha menukarkan bodyguard Ryan dengan Bakri. Dalam kes berasingan, Sarrah bergaduh dengan Taufik yang terlalu kuat cemburu. Bagaimanapun Taufik pandai memujuk, Sarrah akhirnya bersetuju dengan permintaan Taufik supaya perkhidmatan bodyguardnya Bakri dihentikan. Seorang Dato telah datang meminta Nasha menyiasat latar belakang teman wanitanya yang disyaki mempunyai teman lelaki lain.

Metin, yang mengatakan bahawa dia akan melakukan semua jenis bantuan kepada Salih pada mulanya. Kemudian bertunang dengan teman wanita Salih iaitu Sermin, meninggalkan Salih dengan ibunya sendirian. Arzu, bekas tunang Metin, tidak dapat memahami apa yang berlaku. Semasa cuba mencari tahu mengapa Metin berkelakuan sedemikian, Salih dan ibunya, seorang wanita luar biasa, melawat Trkan.

programme.desc: HALIM bersama NINA mengambil MAT di hospital. NINA perasan dirinya diekori satu sosok lembaga. ARIFAH yang sedang membuat persiapan jamuan kepulangan MAT didatangi FAREL dan ECHA yang menghantar makanan. Kemudian disusuli oleh HUSIN yang turut menghantar makanan.MAT yang menyedari isterinya sudah terkena sihir cuba menngubati tetapi gagal. ARIFAH tetap menafikan setiap tekaan MAT demi mengelak MAYA terus berdendam. ARIFAH meninggal dunia akibat serangan penyakit misteri. MAT tidak dapat menerima kematian ARIFAHd an terus membawa diri dari situ. Dendam di hati seolah masih tidak terlerai.

programme.desc: Dua pelajar remaja jatuh cinta dan mempunyai seorang bayi. Tetapi apabila ibu bapa mereka menjauhkan mereka, keadaan menjadi kacau dan gadis itu menjadi semangat pendendam. Tetapi kadang-kadang cinta membuat seseorang buta.

programme.title: J Revolusi
programme.desc: Jay Zulkarnain ialah ketua serangan untuk pasukan khas elit dan maut Malaysia yang dikenali sebagai UTK (Unit Tindakhas), dan dia dan skuad operasinya adalah mimpi ngeri terburuk setiap pengganas. Walau bagaimanapun, seorang pengganas misteri telah menjebak Jay kerana membunuh salah seorang anggota skuadnya, dan juga telah menangkap kakaknya Dian, yang merupakan ejen yang menyamar. Untuk menyelamatkan adiknya, Jay mesti berlumba dengan masa untuk membongkar rahsia dan sebab mengapa pengganas ini cuba memusnahkannya.

programme.title: Kidnap
programme.desc: Mengisahkan hidup Sherry yang sering dikongkong oleh bapanya. Hal ini membuatkan jiwa Sherry memberontak dan ingin mencari kebebasan dalam hidup. Sherry kemudiannya jatuh cinta dengan seorang lelaki bernama Roy. Namun, bapa Sherry tidak merestui cinta mereka dan tidak membenarkan Sherry untuk keluar daripada rumah lagi. Dengan bantuan Zul, bapa Sherry merancang sesuatu untuk merenggangkan hubungan Sherry dengan Roy. Tetapi Roy dan Sherry membalasnya dengan satu penculikan palsu untuk menyedarkan bapa Sherry tentang erti kasih sayang yang sebenar.

programme.title: Nana Tanjung
programme.desc: Seorang duda bernama Nana Kassim membesarkan tiga orang anak perempuannya di Pulau Pinang. Seorang pemuda bernama Akhbar Khan jatuh cinta dengan Khairunisa, anak sulung Nana. Akhbar sanggup menjadi pengawal peribadi Nana untuk selalu berjumpa kekasihnya itu. Pada masa yang sama dia mendapat tahu bahawa Nana mempunyai rancangan lain untuk perkahwinan Khairunisa. Untuk meyakinkan Nana supaya mereka boleh mengahwini pasangan pilihan masing-masing, Akhbar bersama anak-anak Nana memujuknya supaya berkahwin dengan Mami Mumtaz, kekasih lamanya.

programme.title: Siapa Tak Sayang Bini
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kekalutan dua keluarga iaitu Kassim, seorang suami yang garang dan suka mengawal isterinya, Kamisah dan juga Karim, seorang suami yang lembut hati namun dikawal isterinya yang garang, Kasmah. Segalanya bermula apabila Kassim berpindah ke sebelah rumah Karim. Pasangan kaki kontrol cuba menjadi guru dengan mengajar pasangan masing-masing. Keadaan menjadi bertambah kecoh dengan kehadiran Saiful, lelaki bujang yang suka menyibuk hal orang lain. Siapakah yang berjaya mengawal pasangan masing-masing?

programme.title: Putar Alam
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Jeff, Aida dan Ben yang gemar menipu orang untuk mendapatkan wang di Kuala Lumpur. Mereka kemudiannya diupah oleh seseorang untuk mendapatkan saham di sebuah syarikat. Sasaran mereka kali ini ialah Nora, seorang wanita yang baru menjadi pengurus di syarikat itu. Pelbagai kejadian lucu berlaku semasa Jeff mendekati Nora sehingga mereka berdua jatuh cinta.

programme.title: Sepi
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tiga orang yang berasingan mengenal erti cinta, kehilangan dan kesepian. Adam, seorang tukang masak terkenal yang meluaskan kerjayanya dengan mereka hiasan untuk majlis perkahwinan. Tetapi, dengan segala kejayaan itu beliau masih membujang dan belum bertemu jodohnya sendiri. Sufi pula seorang lelaki yang sedang cuba melenyapkan memori kematian isterinya. Akhir sekali, Iman, seorang penulis muda yang menjadikan pentas teater sebagai tapak untuk memahami masa silamnya dan kupasan demi kupasan ke dalam masa depannya sendiri. programme.title: Usop Wilcha Menghonjang Makhluk Muzium

programme.title: Karipap Karipap Cinta
programme.desc: Ali bekerja sebagai jurufoto di syarikat penerbitan majalah jatuh hati kepada Sarah, seorang lulusan Universiti Al-Azhar. Ali panik apabila rakan serumahnya memberitahu keluarga Sarah ingin menjodohkannya dengan seorang ustaz. Untuk memenangi hati Sarah dan keluarganya, Ali terpaksa berbohong dengan mengatakan dia juga merupakan seorang graduan Universiti Al-Azhar. Dalam masa yang sama bos Ali, Dato' Razali Bunari cuba mendedahkan satu skandal yang turut melibatkan bapa Sarah.

programme.title: Tesis
programme.desc: Azira menemani Fatin ke negeri Pahang untuk menyiapkan kajian tesisnya tentang industri pelancongan di sana. Ketika membuat rakaman di sebuah pantai, mereka ternampak dua orang lelaki membuang tubuh seorang wanita ke dalam laut. Mereka berdua kemudiannya dikejar oleh penjahat itu namun dapat melepaskan diri dan segera membuat laporan polis tentang kejadian itu. Fatin yang masih ketakutan itu ingin pulang ke Kuala Lumpur namun Azira meyakinkannya bahawa keadaan mereka selamat dan polis akan memberi bantuan sekiranya mereka diganggu. Seperti yang Fatin jangka, penjahat itu kini mengekorinya sehingga dia dan Fatin melarikan diri ke dalam hutan. Tanpa disedari, mereka berdua telah terperangkap dalam satu sindiket.

programme.title: 4 Madu
programme.desc: Azlan, seorang pekerja biasa di sebuah chalet telah menerima surat yang memintanya hadir ke pejabat guaman di Kuala Lumpur. Setibanya di ibu kota, Azlan telah diperkenalkan dengan adik tirinya, Azrul untuk pertama kali dalam hidupnya. Di pejabat guaman itu, Encik Zahrin Ishak membacakan wasiat yang ditinggalkan oleh arwah ayah mereka. Segala harta yang bernilai 50 juta ringgit akan menjadi hak milik mereka sekiranya mereka dapat memenuhi syarat-syarat yang terkandung dalam wasiat itu. Antara perkara yang perlu dilaksanakan ialah, mereka berdua harus mencari isteri dalam tempoh 3 minggu serta calon isteri itu mestilah seorang anak yatim piatu.

programme.title: Chantek
programme.desc: Chantek, seorang pembantu rumah dari Indonesia yang terpaksa menyamar sebagai lelaki untuk menenteramkan AD yang masih fobia dengan perempuan. Lama-kelamaan kerana kebaikan AD dan kemesraan mereka berdua, Chantek terpaksa mendedahkan rahsianya. Walaupun marah, AD sedia memaafkannya kerana kejujuran Chantek membantu memulihkannya dan akhirnya mereka berdua telah jatuh cinta. Namun hati Chantek berubah setelah dia terasa dipergunakan oleh AD sebagai bahan latihan filemnya. Berjayakah AD bertemu dan memenangi hati Chantek kembali?

programme.title: A Lifetime Treasure
programme.desc: A peaceful home for the elderly is under attack when a gangster and his cronies attempt to set up traps to take over the home! Little did they know that the five elderlies residing in the home have amazing talents to take them head on.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: We are Family
programme.desc: Struggling as an extra, Chi Kwong joins a rent-a-family company run by Carlos and aspiring actress Catherine, and rent themselves out as make-believe relatives. As they surrogate different families, they unravel the complexities of family relationships, forging deeper connections along the way.

programme.title: The Monkey is Back
programme.desc: The savior of the people, Stone Monkey, has given hope to a desperate little girl which he promises to realize. Years later, Stone Monkey is defeated in a battle with the three-eyed God of War, causing him to lose his power and falls into the mortal world. Can he fulfill his promise to the girl and stop the God of Wood from destroying earth?

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the Gang of Five in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Dream Lover
programme.desc: Ka Shing meets Kitty one day and they fall quickly in love. However, Kitty disappears shortly and when they meet years later, she is already married. To comfort himself, Ka Shing asks a mystic master to let Kitty appear in his dreams so that he can be with her constantly, even though she can only be his dream lover...

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: Imprisoned 2: There Is No Escape From Fate
programme.desc: Hong Kong businessman Yu and his secretary travel abroad for business meetings. When the secretary is killed in their hotel, Yu is arrested. Despite pleading not guilty, Yu is imprisoned in a cruel multinational prison where the warden enjoys torturing prisoners, and he must find a way to escape from this dark and deadly prison to survive.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: The Knight of Shadows: Between Yin and Yang
programme.desc: Pu Song Ling, a legendary demon hunter, is asked to investigate a case involving missing teenage village girls with disciple, Constable Yan Fei. The duo leads a group of little monsters to help with the investigation, and in their search for the truth, they accidentally discover a mysterious love between a knight and a female ghost.

programme.title: We are Family
programme.desc: Struggling as an extra, Chi Kwong joins a rent-a-family company run by Carlos and aspiring actress Catherine, and rent themselves out as make-believe relatives. As they surrogate different families, they unravel the complexities of family relationships, forging deeper connections along the way.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Hell Hole
programme.desc: The movie features three horror stories in different era: a pregnant woman haunted by a ghost sacrifices her life to save her baby; a boy commits suicide after being bullied by four medical students and his spirit returns for revenge; some company staff are haunted after they open a box of used clothes, releasing a more than 20-year resentment.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon (2020)
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kongs legendary detective?

programme.title: Shining for One Thing
programme.desc: Zhang Wan Sen plans to confess his crush on Lin Bei Xing after the college entrance exam, but an accident changes everything tragically. As Zhang feels helpless and devastated, he fortuitously travels back in time with Lin Bei Xing before the accident happens. Can he make amends and convey his regrets this time?

programme.title: God of Gamblers 2
programme.desc: A new chapter of the highly successful "God of Gamblers". The legend's disciple Andy Lau is now rising in the gambling world as the "Knight of Gamblers"; clashing with another gambling icon, the wild psychic Stephen Chow (aka "Saint of Gamblers") who wants to follow the God. They mix like oil and water in a series of tricks and mishaps, but are forced to join hands against their master's nemesis on the gambling table.

programme.title: Home Sweet Home
programme.desc: A school bus accident kills almost everyone on board. The bus driver got injured and partially lost his memory while rescuing one of the boys. To thank the driver, the boys dad, Wang, brings him to live with the family in their basement. However, the driver soon discovers strange behaviours from the Wangs which seem to be related to the accident.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Night and Fog
programme.desc: Following The Way We Are, this is based on a true story happening in Tin Shui Wai. It revolves around an older, unemployed Hong Kong man, his young Mainland wife and their two daughters. Their lives, unfortunately, are anything but easy, and the shocking conclusion raises issues about the plight of the socially deprived lower class.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Three bizarre tales intertwine in this horror satire set against the housing crisis of Hong Kong, where soaring property prices have driven dwellers to take every insane effort necessary to secure a cramped space, even if it means sharing the same roof with the dead!

programme.title: Marrying Mr Perfect
programme.desc: Winnie is dumped by her boyfriend in her late twenties and unknowingly meets Koo, a ruthless tycoon in business and a playboy. Koo temporarily switches identities with his driver for security reason and falls for Winnie as she is the first girl to love him for who he is. What will happen when Winnie know Koos real identity?

programme.title: Detrimental
programme.desc: You Ji Ren is a blind man who works at a factory in an outlying island. When the factory is cut off from the outside world by a hurricane one day, a monster appears and turns whoever sees it into black shadows. As You cannot see the monster, he is able to help other coworkers leave safely and fight to kill the monster!

programme.title: Golden Chickensss
programme.desc: Ah Kam is now a mama-san leading a team of young prostitutes to service the rich and famous, and she always aims to fulfil every clients needs. When Ah Kams ex-lover, a triad boss, encounters difficulties adapting to a new Hong Kong after his release from a long imprisonment, she helps him get back on his feet to lead a normal life.

programme.title: Maoshan Heavenly Master
programme.desc: Prisoner Chi flees away under Master Zhangs custody, causing the latter to be expelled from his clan. On his way to find Chi, Master Zhang arrives at a place where many people vanish for no reason. He soon discovers that it is Chi who captures them in his training to become a serpent demon. The war between human and demon has just begun!

programme.title: Break Up Club
programme.desc: Joe (Jaycee Chan) is a 20-something slacker who only takes one thing seriously: his on-and-off girlfriend Flora (Fiona Sit). After their latest breakup, Joe goes to an audition for a documentary by director Barbara Wong (the director, playing herself). Handed a camera, Joe records his discovery of a magical website that reunites him with Flora at the price of breaking up his best friend (Patrick Tang) and his girlfriend. However, despite the efficiency of the website, Joe's refusal to change his immature ways and Flora's attraction to a talented graffiti artist (Hayama Hiro) threatens to break them up once more.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Lin Dai stars in this romantic classic as a nightclub singer who falls for a young architect. When he suffers grave financial difficulty, she does the unthinkable to help him.

programme.title: Legend of the Bat
programme.desc: It is rumoured that people can buy anything they desire on the mysterious Island of Bats so long as they have money. The charismatic swordsman Chu Liu Xiang and his friend travel to the island to seek answers but realize they are not the only ones who want to unveil the mystery of this place.

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read and filmed novel in Chinese history, this sumptuous version was said to be the most successful one. Loh Tihs looks, demeanour and aura in her portrayal of Lin Dai Yu has won her the epithet "Classic Beauty".

programme.title: The Killer
programme.desc: Hsieh Choun, the Black Dragon, is in trouble with the police since Wang Sien Tien's gang is helping them; he is no longer free to conduct his drugs shipments out of the port freely as he used to. He buys more thugs and killers to dispose of the young upstart, and soon Wang is in dire straits, in the port of Hong Kong.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content; yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu Lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun Yang.

programme.title: Clan Of The White Lotus
programme.desc: The head of White Lotus Clan, Lo, is a highly skilled martial artist who supports the Qing government and helps destroy the rebellion group. Hung from Shaolin who kills Los brother, is being hunted and hides in another rebel Hus house. The clan attacks at night killing Hu and his sister, but Hung manages to get Hus pregnant wife to safety.

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: Ambush
programme.desc: Constable Wen Chao Fan and his father are framed for a jewel robbery they did not commit. On the run from the law and becoming a wanted fugitive, Wen must recover the jewels in order to clear his family name, but unfortunately he is not the only one seeking the stolen jewels...

programme.title: Return of the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three sworn brothers, Zhang, Huang and Ma ends when Ma gives in to corruption and falls for Huang's wife, eventually leading to a bloody ending.

programme.title: Moods Of Love
programme.desc: This Song Dynasty period piece about how far one would go for love (or lust) has two tales. The first involves a devilish magistrate who tries to tempt a Buddhist monk out of his self-professed celibacy by hiring a pretty prostitute. The second is the tragic tale of an exploited young girl who is forced to work in an unscrupulous couples brothel.

programme.title: The Female Prince
programme.desc: Hsiao's stepmother frames her fianc Lung when he refuses to forfeit their engagement and sends him to prison. To save him, Hsiao disguises as Lung to take the Imperial exam and ranks first place. Impressed by Hsiao, the Emperor weds the Princess to 'him'. When Hsiao comes clean on their wedding night, she persuades the Princess to follow a plan

programme.title: Duel For Gold
programme.desc: Six swordsmen, including two sisters and their husbands, a ranger and a security man, are trying to steal a million gold taels from the Fu Lai Treasury House, not knowing that one of them is actually an undercover hero. In their quest, they have to double-cross and outwit one another...

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: King Gambler
programme.desc: This film was actually a lively forerunner to the gambling film craze, which eventually swept Asian cinema. Here, it's cardsharp versus cardsharp with a lot more kung-fu action, in a battle of wits and fists to become the king of the casino. The double stings and triple crosses raise in complexity and imagination until what started as an unusual box office risk became a top ten hit of 1976.

programme.title: Let's Fall In Love
programme.desc: Da Yung, the son of a rich entrepreneur, meets Lian Lian, the niece of a kindergarten principal by chance. They get into a misunderstanding at the first meeting, causing Da Yung to lose his wallet. Further misunderstanding occurs when he tries to use her to act as his fianc, in order to drive away two women whom he does not like

programme.title: Magnificent Wanderers
programme.desc: Lin and his two friends are traveling patriots who vow to stand up against violence and fight for justice. They meet a rich young man Chu by chance one day and the four become best friends. When a foreign prince plots to possess Chus family fortune and goes after him, Lin and friends go all out to help Chu fight against the villain.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: The Brave Archer 2
programme.desc: Knowing Guo Jing has won Huang Rongs hand in marriage using the kung fu learned from Jiu Yin manual, Ouyang Feng captures Huang and agrees to release her only if Guo can dictate the content of the manual. Will Guo give in to the threat?

programme.title: Big Times for the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again

programme.title: The Crimson Charm
programme.desc: In attempting to rescue some innocent people, swordsman Chiang Tzu-chao (Fang Mien) slays the son of Tsao Kang (Wang Hsia), leader of the ruthless Crimson Charm gang.The enraged father promises vengeance on the day of Chiang's 60th birthday...

programme.title: The Younger Generation
programme.desc: A tragic tale about a young girl who gets married and has five kids. When she and her husband die, leaving all five kids behind to fend for themselves, the eldest child is forced to be sold into prostitution to feed the other four.

programme.title: Purple Darts
programme.desc: A girl vows to take revenge for her parents who were murdered by four outlaws when she was only a baby. To do so, she trains hard at martial arts and teams up with a swordsman and a couple to finally kill them all.

programme.title: To Kill a Jaguar
programme.desc: Set in 1920s Shanghai, a village girl journeys to the big city in search of her father and meets her childhood friend Jaguar, who works for the mob boss Kam. In a world controlled by the mobs, it is a test of survival for all as Jaguar allies himself with ace gunman Ko Tang, to take over Kams empire.

programme.title: Clans of Intrigue
programme.desc: Heroic outlaw Chu Liu Xiang is dining with his friend Monk Wu Hua, when Gong from the Holy Water Palace appears and accuses Chu of stealing the holy water from her Palace and using it for various murders. Chu denies, and is given a month to find the murderer or be killed by Gong. To prove his innocence, Chu decides to investigate the case

programme.title: The Golden Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman supreme Cheng Pei-pei (Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon) teams up with director/writer/actor Lo Wei (director of Bruce Lee and Jackie Chans first major movies) for an evocative and terrific Martial arts world adventure consisting of a missing blade and a deadly sect of men-hating swordswomen.

programme.title: Diau Charn
programme.desc: In the Han Dynasty, the tyrannical Prime Minister Dong Zuo takes control of the country, so Minister Wang plots to take him down using Diau Charns beauty. Wang arranges for her to be Dongs concubine as he knows Dongs adopted son Lu Bu is in love with her, turning them against each other. Lu Bu ends up killing Dong Zuo to be with Diau Charn.

programme.title: The Black Butterfly
programme.desc: Kwan leads a double life as a waitress and as an infamous outlaw skilled in martial arts, The Black Butterfly. When she steals a cache of gold from the Five Devils Rock bandits, she soon has the bandits, and the government, on her tail.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: Clan of Amazons
programme.desc: The martial arts world is plunged into terror when a mysterious figure known as the 'Embroidery Bandit' starts to attack convoys of precious materials. Seemingly unstoppable, the frightened clans decide to call on the expertise of Lu Xiao Feng, an inquisitive fighter and detective to capture the culprit.

programme.title: My Name Ain't Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated. It is not until she encounters the triad boss Ying that she finally found someone to count on.

programme.title: Heroes Two
programme.desc: Shaolin disciple Hung escapes from the burning temple after it is attacked by the Qing army and is badly wounded. He is handed over to the Qing soldiers by Fang as he mistakes Hung for a bandit. When Fang realizes his mistakes, he tries all ways to help Hung escape so that they can team up to fight the Qing army together.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep31
programme.desc: Snow Day / Guy Misses Out - It only snows one day a year in Troll Village, and Poppy, Branch, and Smidge want to make the most of it. Poppy tries to finally get in a hit in her annual snowball fight with Peppy; Branch is determined to make up for the snow days he missed while in his bunker; Smidge tries to get first place in all of the Snow Day competitions./While waiting for the perfect time to make his big entrance at a party, Guy misses the formation of an inside joke. The Snack Pack tells him he just had to be there, but Guy sets out to understand the joke and get in on the laughter.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep32
programme.desc: Scrap to the Future / Bringing Up Birdy - As shes preparing for the Hearts & Crafts Festival, Poppy finds a mysterious scrapbook that seems to predict the future and it shows the festival being a disaster! She and Branch set out to prevent the predictions from coming true. But is there a downside to being over prepared?/When a nest full of just-hatched baby birds imprint on Branch, he must overcome his fear of birds in order to raise them right.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep33
programme.desc: Close Encounters Of The Mort Kind - When Mort is abducted by "aliens", King Julien teams with Clover, Maurice and Hector to investigate why he's not the one being abducted.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep34
programme.desc: The Butterfly War - King Julien declares a war against butterflies to raise his kingdom's spirit, but when the village is destroyed he decides to hold a peace summit.

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep7
programme.desc: Lucky And The Cowboy Next Door - When the annual roundup and town dance brings cowboy Javier to Miradero Lucky finds a new friend who can teach her and Spirit a new trick.

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep8
programme.desc: Lucky And The Pie P.I. - Mysteries collide when horse thieves strike Miradero at the same time as a pie thief strikes the church bake sale while the adults try to keep the horse thieves at bay Lucky is determined to find out who stole the pies.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep19
programme.desc: Stuff / Campout - When Kelp and Scallop discover Mr. Pearly has a cave full of stuff they help him to realize it could help a lot of other sea creatures. / When the group goes camping, Kelp helps Ollie learn that even though it didnt go exactly as planned, they can still have loads of fun.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep2
programme.desc: The Sleepover Save / The Very Hungry Vacuum - Marcus is having his first sleepover and Phoebe is concerned that Marcus may be nervous so Phoebe sets out to make sure he has the best first sleepover ever. / When Athenas magical jump rope gets sucked up by the familys new robot vacuum, she loses confidence in her abilities, only to learn that her real abilities are already inside her.

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep10
programme.desc: Night Of The Living Croods / Spoonful Of Soo-Gar - When The Croods experience the first-ever sugar-rush, they're hooked on the delicious new food; Grug is labeled a zombie after taking the first nap.

programme.title: Legend of the Boneknapper Ep1
programme.desc: Legend Of The Boneknapper Dragon - Hiccup and the gang join Gobber on a quest to find a legendary boneknapper dragon.

programme.title: Gift of the Night Fury Ep1
programme.desc: Dragons:Gift Of The Night Fury - As the village of Berk prepares for its winter holiday, the resident dragons all inexplicably fly away.

programme.title: Book of Dragons Ep1
programme.desc: Book Of Dragons - Join Hiccup and his friends as they explore and add to their primary reference about dragons.

programme.title: Dawn of the Dragon Racers Ep1
programme.desc: Dawn Of The Dragon Racers - The "How to Train Your Dragon" adventure continues when a hunt for lost sheep turns into a fierce, fun-filled competition.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep13
programme.desc: End of the Dragon Master - Po, the kids, and the new Panda Guardians must work together to defeat Jindiao once and for all, and get a visit from an unlikely source

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep14
programme.desc: Journey to the East - Feeling a little bored with their new hero life, Po and the kids are excited to accept an important invitation to the Forbidden City. Meanwhile, there's a curious disturbance deep in Panda Village...

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep15
programme.desc: Curse of the Monkey King - Po and the Kids take a shortcut to the boat bound for the Forbidden City, and are waylaid by a tricky monkey. Zhizhu informs Mayor Li of some distressing sounds coming from the Wellspring.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep16
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Harmful Horrors of the Harrowing Hiveschool - After injecting all the teachers with bee DNA, the Melvins run the new "hivemind" of the school. But Ms. Ribble is accidently injected with too much "Bee- NA" and becomes the queen bee, overpowering the Melvins' control. George, Harold and the recently re-hired Vice Principal Krupp must work with the Melvins and stop her from turning everyone into her Zombees.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep17
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Preposterous Pulverizing of the Pestering Poopacabra - In hopes of raising their grades so they can go to Lake Summer Camp, George and Harold must teach Ratrick, their assigned rat, a simple task. But Ratrick runs away into the sewers where he is doused with toxic waste and transformed into Poopacabra! It's now up to the boys and Captain Underpants to stop the beast before it takes over Piqua with its stench, and more importantly, ruins the boys' chances to go to Lake Summer Camp.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep18
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Dastardlys Deed of the Devious Diddlysaurus - George and Harold decide to do an extra credit project on dinosaurs to help their chances of getting summer camp-worthy grades. When Melvin brings in a dinosaur frozen in ice, the boys try to get rid of it. But the ice thaws and they meet Diddlysaurus, a prankster raptor who's huge fans of the boys. He offers to help them with their project if he can pull pranks with them, but when the pranks go too far, the boys and Captain Underpants have to deal with the dino.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep36
programme.desc: Chummy Sparklestone / Giggleyum - When the Funtime Factory stops producing one of their frosting flavors, Poppy sets out to create a replacement. But is her new flavor, Giggleyum too delicious?/During a Troll mystery party, Cooper has the role of detective. But when the party is over, Detective Cooper now Chummy Sparklestone refuses to break character, and hes causing problems around the village!

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep37
programme.desc: Glamping / A Flower for Poppy - Branch is excited to take the Troll children camping with him. But when Guy Diamond arrives at the camp site with glamping gear, the kids decide they prefer Guys plush method of camping to Branchs insistence on roughing it./Poppys the most amazing gift-giver in Troll Village, and the Snack Pack are determined to finally gift her something as good as her birthday. So when Poppy off-handedly mentions her favorite rare flower, her friends set out to find it for her- but who will get to gift it?

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep38
programme.desc: The Partier's Apprentice / Hair Ball - Guy is running himself ragged trying to be the life of the party for every party in Troll Village. When Poppy suggests he train an apprentice, it seems like the solution to his problems! Until his apprentice starts to surpass his partying skills/When Smidge accidentally agrees to go with both Milton and Guy to the Trolls fanciest event, the Hair Ball, she must navigate the difficulties of her situation with help from her friends.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep39
programme.desc: Pyg & Tam - Boss Baby encounters a new threat to Baby Love: an adorable Baby TV show starring Pyg the Pygmy Goat, Tam the Tamandua, and their host Maria-Maria. Boss is told not to go to Corporate War by Board Baby Emiliano, so Boss tries to provoke his enemies to make the first move.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep40
programme.desc: Conference Room B - Boss promises Tim he'll help make their parents' anniversary present, but after Puppy Co. and Baby Corp's fight over a conference room escalates, he sends Hendershot is his stead. Hendershot, armed with a file on all of Tim's wants and needs, tries to keep Tim happy.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep41
